description:
What: Add all group-chat protocol types to core/src/protocol.rs.

Algorithm:
1. Add to rpc_methods module: GROUP_CREATE='group_create', GROUP_ADD='group_add', GROUP_SEND='group_send', GROUP_LEAVE='group_leave', GROUP_LIST='group_list', GROUP_DELIVER='group_deliver'
2. Add to rpc_errors module: GROUP_NOT_FOUND: i32 = -32011, NOT_A_MEMBER: i32 = -32012
3. Add structs (matching existing style — serde_as Base64 for Vec<u8> payloads, all fields pub):
   - GroupCreateParams { name: String }
   - GroupCreateResult { group_id: String, name: String }
   - GroupAddParams { group_id: String, member_pub_id: String }
   - GroupSendParams { group_id: String, payload: Vec<u8> }  // Base64
   - GroupSendResult { message_id: String }
   - GroupLeaveParams { group_id: String }
   - GroupInfo { group_id: String, name: String, member_count: u64, created_at: String }
   - GroupListResult { groups: Vec<GroupInfo> }
   - GroupDeliverParams { from: String, group_id: String, payload: Vec<u8> }  // Base64

Defensive rules:
- No Default impl on structs with Vec<u8>
- All derives: Debug + Clone + Serialize + Deserialize
- Match existing #[serde_as] pattern for Base64 payloads

Team: standard R+I+T
